org.aion.api.type

Class MsgRsp

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aion.api.type.MsgRsp

  • public class MsgRsp
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the transaction status including the execution status and the API session hash. 
     param preStatus
      the transaction previous execute status.
 param status
      the transaction execute status.
 param msgHash
      it's for the internal Java API use to recognize this class is belong to which transaction API operation.
 param txHash
      the class Hash256 represent to the 32bytes transaction ID
 param txResult
      the class ByteArrayWrapper represent the transaction result.
 param txDeploy
      the class ByteArrayWrapper represent the deploy result if it is a contract deploy.
    Author:
    Jay Tseng
    See Also:
    ITx.sendTransaction(org.aion.api.type.TxArgs), ITx.sendRawTransaction(org.aion.base.util.ByteArrayWrapper),
